show.description: Beizzati, maar, aur thukraaya gaya — Jackson ki zindagi mein izzat naam ki cheez hi nahi thi. Ek factory worker, jisko duniya sirf majdoori ke laayak samajhti thi. Lekin uski khamoshi ke peeche ek raaz tha… Woh ek trillion-dollar empire ka chhupa hua vaaris tha. Aur jab wahi log jo uska mazak udaate the, uska asli sach jaante hain… Tab shuru hoti hai asli kahani. Dhokhe, badle aur ek zabardast comeback ki kahani — Yeh sirf ek safar nahi, ek jung hai.
